<lb ed="X" n="0540a13"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a10"/><l>奉請北方成就佛</l><l>其身黑色放光明</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a14"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a11"/><l>手印執持妙降魔</l><l>眾等志心歸命禮</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a15"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a12"/><l>今將密語遶香壇</l><l>憑此結成羯磨界</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a16"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a13"/><l>奉請中方毗盧佛</l><l>其身黃色放光明</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a17"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a14"/><l>手印執持千輻輪</l><l>眾等志心歸命禮</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a18"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a15"/><l>今將密語遶香壇</l><l>憑此結成瑜伽界</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a19"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a16"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540a1901">集福迎祥幢幡為寶蓋。振動金鈴。殄滅諸</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a20"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a17"/><list><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2001">阿閦</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2003">持國</item>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a21"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048a18"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2101">寶生</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2103">增長</item></list>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a22"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048b01"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540a2201">妖恠。彌陀佛如來慈悲甚廣大。廣目天王來。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a23"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048b02"/><list><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2301">成就</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2303">多聞</item>
<lb ed="X" n="0540a24"/><lb ed="R129" n="0048b03"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2401">毗盧</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2403">大梵</item></list>
